5:
Okay... Well now what am I
supposed to do?
9:
I mean, it's probably too late for me
to... Oh!
14: Stella! Just the girl I wanted to see.
26:
Don't think you're hot stuff just
because you met Stella before I did.
30: I... I don't think I was?
34:
Yeah? Then why're you hoggin' her
all the damn time, anyway? Just
what are you two—
46:
Ah... No fighting during meals, right?
Tch. Yeah, I know.
50:
Sorry. I guess it's cool if you join us
this time, Chef.
52:
Actually, could I ask you guys about
something?
57: You want to register with the guild?
61:
You guys have some sorta
connection with that Lilie character,
right? Mind putting in a good word
for me?
65:
You mean you haven't done so
yourself already?
69:
I don't got a clean slate like you,
Mister Unlikely Protagonist. They'd
probably take me in for questioning
instead, I bet.
74:
I see. So is that why you prefer to
remain in the Kaleidoscope so often?
78:
Yeah... Somethin' like that. I mean, it's
pretty hard to earn a livin' out there
nowadays without goin' through the
damn Guild.
81:
So I'm askin' a real favor here. Could
you do somethin' about this for me?
If it's money you need, I'll come up
with it somehow!
85:
Don't worry about payment or
anything—we'd be glad to introduce
you.
90:
Yays! It'd be my pleasure to sign you
up!
99:
Are you familiar with our
rehabilitation program? Even if you
have a sketchy past, the Guild would
be more than happy to get you
sorted out—under our supervision of
course.
101:
Once we've determined that you're
willing to reform, we'll take you off
probation and you'll be able to take
on jobs like any other member.
102:
All former miscreants looking for a
fresh start are welcome! Evil outlaws
and villains excluded.
107: Huh... I never knew about that.
111:
It's actually a new program—started
by yours truly! Hehe.
115:
So you're sayin'... that I can sign up
to be a Guild adventurer?
120: You sure can! Welcome to the Guild!
125: Awesome! I... I can't believe it!
133: Let's gooooo! Bring it on, baby!
137:
Heh, she's pretty fired up. But we
ain't no slouches either!
151:
Sorry, Stella! You're still supposed to
be under my protection, aren'tcha?
166:
It was thanks to you that I was able
to turn things around...
169:
The world's much easier to change
than you think, isn't it?
179:
Heh. Well, what are we waitin' for?
There's worlds to explore... and
money to be made!
183:
And more of Alk's cookin' to eat, on
top of that!
